///                 - *Children:*
///                     - **Head**
///                     - **Body**
///                     - **Hands**
///                     - **Feet**
///                     - **Shadow**
///                     - *Shared components:*
///                         - SpriteRenderer
///             - **CharacterTop**
///                 - *Children:*
///                     - **Head**
///                     - **Body**
///                     - **Hands**
///                     - **Feet**
///                     - **Shadow**
///                     - *Shared components:*
///                         - SpriteRenderer
///             - **LocalPlayerIndicator**
///                 - *components*
///                     - Transform

